headline: Humana (NYSE:HUM) Lowers Full-Year Earnings Guidance
summary: Humana (NYSE:HUM) recently reported robust first-quarter earnings with significant increases in revenue and net income, highlighting its strong operational performance. Nevertheless, the company lowered its full-year earnings guidance, which, along with prevailing market trends, contributed to its share price decline of 10.22% over the last week.
